{"tid":529600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳皇馬招手 沙拿：喺利記好開心！","createTime":"2018-01-15T02:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T04:18:18.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25f526260ef9821b0b99c3f3542ae0cc27fde2f8","tid":529600,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"菲臘比古天奴嘅離開可以講係傷盡利迷嘅心，但依家一單都唔夠，重有傳皇家馬德里睇中咗穆罕默德沙拿，想今個月帶走佢。沙拿就向利迷派定心丸，話喺利記過得好開心，「要傳咩就由得佢!」<br />\n<br />\n沙拿早前接受訪問，提及有關自己嘅轉會傳聞：「我都聽過好多傳聞，但呢啲都唔會影響我。利記對我好好，我係利記嘅人，喺晏菲路亦都過得好開心。要傳咩就由得佢啦！」<br />\n不過利迷唔好咁老定，查實古天奴走之前都講過好多次話留喺利記好開心，上年重續埋長約，世事從來都係變幻莫測！"},{"pid":"4727930df6cd9344e1c6e97b0de8dc50c15dac0a","tid":529600,"uid":33728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"25號"},{"pid":"dd55546ca1f40f1c9cd60133e09856d273b26a1f","tid":529600,"uid":28758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"蝗真係要既話，佢咪又一樣學古天奴貼錢走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8975e415a526e9a318e9f61f4c9b1c5474afb1e6","tid":529600,"uid":18271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"上一手同事都係咁講<br />\n上一手同事都係咁講"},{"pid":"2bee077bfd4fdeb9878f9ef957a31c42e72683d4","tid":529600,"uid":71694,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"皇仲廢過利啦轉黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79754087c7282fed729bde422188be218efe7798","tid":529600,"uid":141421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:04:34.000Z","msg":"我地利記唔係selling club"},{"pid":"9613026d347b17caa07e8ff599234da56930094f","tid":529600,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"吉夭如上年1月講既野<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.itv.com/news/update/2017-01-28/coutinho-walking-in-footsteps-of-liverpool-legends/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv